channel.title: OS-Reborn - OSRS Economy - OSRS Data
channel.description:
[CENTER]OS-Reborn is Economy Server with an awesome community! Community is always friendly and helpful to everyone. OS-Reborn is OSRS based server and got great features. OS-Reborn was launched on 12/20/2015 and it's officially online now. We are very-very glad to hear all of the suggestions and things what should be added.
We got a lot of things to offer you! All working 20 skills, great PKing system, Ironman Mode, Zulrah, a lot of bosses in Wilderness and in safezone aswell and lots of more! There are also Achievemets what you can complete and get rewarded! You are more than welcome to join us and have fun in general. Come and even try it! OS-Reborn is rapidly growning. We're currently looking for some experienced staff members (Community Managers/Helpers) that are mature and capable for the spot! (no staffhunters). We are putting a lot of time to server and adding a lot of things and fixing everything what is possible.
Anyways, I'm not man of thousand words or even good at making advertising thread so this was just a quickly made thread! Come and see us at!
[URL=http://"http://os-reborn.net/forums/forum.php"]OS-Reborn Forums[/URL]
[b]Quick Feature list[/b]
OSRS Data 15+ Bosses Ironman Mode Bank tabs, bank searching etc Zulrah Corporeal Beast Fully Working Clan Chat 30+ Achievements All boss pets Most of the OSRS Content
And lots of more, come and see.
